CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

August 6, 2007

[Cite as 08/06/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-3963.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-0683. In re Application of Holbrook.

This cause came on for consideration upon the filing by Joel R. Rovito of a motion to withdraw as counsel for the applicant. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by this court that the motion is granted.
